      "heading": "‘All of Us Strangers’",
      "note": "full spoilers",
      "films": [
        {
          "title": "All of Us Strangers",
          "year": 2023,
          "note": "Andrew Haigh's ghost-story queer romance, adapted from Taichi Yamada's novel and shot in Haigh's own childhood home. Andrew Scott's Adam visits his long-dead parents and falls for a neighbor; a movie of big feelings that Sean thinks gets smaller the harder you dissect it."
        }
      ]
